SUMMARY:🎸✨ Road Trip to Niagara Falls: Collective Soul Live ✨🎸$5
 0 ticket and transport
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\n🎸
 🚗 **Sunday Road Trip to Niagara Falls: Collective Soul Live!** 🚗🎸
 \n**Sunday\, March 29**\n\nJoin us for an unforgettable Sunday night getaw
 ay to **Niagara Falls** to see **Collective Soul** live at Fallsview Casin
 o Resort!\n\n$50 includes your concert ticket AND round-trip transportatio
 n. An unbeatable value.\n\nTravel together in a comfortable **Kia Soul**\,
  equipped with **snow tires** and **SiriusXM**\, and enjoy a relaxed\, mus
 ic-filled road trip before an epic night of ‘90s alt-rock and chart-topp
 ing hits.\n\n***\n\n### 🎶 **About the Show**\n\nCollective Soul rose to
  fame with massive hits like *“Shine\,” “December\,”* and *“The 
 World I Know.”* Known for their melodic rock sound\, powerful vocals\, a
 nd energetic live performances\, they continue to deliver crowd-pleasing s
 hows packed with nostalgia and sing-along moments.\n\n🔗 **Event details
 :**\n[https://fallsviewcasinoresort.com/events-and-promotions/schedule-of-
 events/collective-soul.html](https://fallsviewcasinoresort.com/events-and-
 promotions/schedule-of-events/collective-soul.html)\n\n***\n\n### 🕓 **S
 chedule**\n\n* **4:00 PM** – Depart Toronto from outside Christie Statio
 n\n* **7:00 PM** – Concert starts\n* **\\~11:30PM** – Return to Toront
 o\n\n***\n\n### 🚗 **What’s Included**\n\n* 🎟️ Concert ticket\n* 
 🚘 Round-trip transportation in a Kia Soul\n* 🎶 SiriusXM music for th
 e drive\n\n***\n\n### 💲 **Cost**\n\n**$50 total** (includes ticket and 
 transportation)\n👉 **Payment required in advance**\n\nPlease e-transfer
  $50 to: nicolasbello@yahoo.com\n\n**Your spot is confirmed only once paym
 ent is received.**\n\n***\n\nSpace is limited\, so please RSVP **only if y
 ou’re fully committed**\, as tickets and transportation are arranged in 
 advance.\nLet’s close out the weekend with a great concert\, an easy roa
 d trip\, and some classic alt-rock vibes! 🎸✨
